Code has been updated for Python 3.9

How to run the application:

    * Install Python 3.9 and create a Python 39 virtual environment and activate it. (Path variable in Windows)

    * install the requirements of the project:
      
          pip install -r requirements.txt

    * run the migrations to create the schema

          python manage.py migrate

    * create a superuser (this will be the user capable of creating lotteries,
      generating tickets for them, etc.)

          python manage.py createsuperuser
          Specify Username and Password (Save at safe place.)

    * for a test run, use the following command:

          python manage.py runserver
		  

This version is inherited from below URL
https://github.com/jerojasro/lottery.git